Siberia and Manchuria; winters to s Asia and n Australia

Known to breed in western Siberia near Tara in the valley of the Irtysh, the region about Barnaul in the vallpy of the Ob; in Transbaikalia in the Argun Valley and in northwestern and central Mongolia. On migration and in winter to China, Japan, northern India, Burma and Indo-Chinese countries.
